s%2F76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F76becb14-2b44-4b9c-81e9-4cd93727ca8a_560x306.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/products/databriefs/db464.htm">疾病预防控制中心</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>他对于“年轻”部分的看法也是正确的。最近，老年人的自杀率实际上有所下降，而年轻人的自杀率却持续不断上升： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F96712232-0187-40f2-9ae4-121507beace9_560x305.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F96712232-0187-40f2-9ae4-121507beace9_560x305.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F96712232-0187-40f2-9ae4-121507beace9_560x305.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F96712232-0187-40f2-9ae4-121507beace9_560x305.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F96712232-0187-40f2-9ae4-121507beace9_560x305.jpeg" width="560" height="305" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/96712232-0187-40f2-9ae4-121507beace9_560x305.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:305,&quot;width&quot;:560,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:35006,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F96712232-0187-40f2-9ae4-121507beace9_560x305.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F96712232-0187-40f2-9ae4-121507beace9_560x305.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F96712232-0187-40f2-9ae4-121507beace9_560x305.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F96712232-0187-40f2-9ae4-121507beace9_560x305.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/products/databriefs/db464.htm">疾病预防控制中心</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>我不知道这个国家需要做什么来阻止自杀流行，但尽量不让年轻人失望似乎是一个很好的一般原则。</p><p>最后，还有取消文化。安东尼唱道：</p><blockquote><p>天知道他们都只是想完全控制<br>想知道你在想什么，想知道你在做什么</p></blockquote><p>这确实是事实；人们都是爱管闲事的人，想要控制你的生活。但我怀疑里士满北部的富人本身是否比普通无聊的中产阶级青少年更感兴趣。事实上，这里的问题只是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/its-not-cancel-culture-its-cancel-ade">互联网</a>——过去每个人的行为和思想都被小镇上好管闲事的邻居控制，然后我们度过了辉煌的几十年，汽车和城市生活让你可以独自生活，远离喧嚣。从窥探的目光中，然后社交媒体的出现，让世界再次变成了一堆小镇。叹。</p><p>但这不是阴谋。鉴于技术的进步，这只是我们必须适应的事情。越来越多的人将离开推特等集中式社交媒体网络，回到小组论坛和讨论，“管好自己的事”将在美国卷土重来，成为一种道德灵丹妙药。</p><p>不管怎样，总的来说，我对奥利弗·安东尼所唱的大部分问题表示同情。我们确实生活在一个工作时间长、工资往往很低且停滞不前的国家。肥胖和自杀已成为日益严重的社会弊病。如果仅仅因为这些抱怨来自右翼民粹主义者而拒绝接受，那将是一个很大的错误。但像右翼民粹主义那样，将福利计划或不值得的福利接受者视为这些弊病的根源，这是严重误导的。减税并不能解决美国的问题。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-economics-of-rich-men-north-of?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-economics-of-rich-men-north-of?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=s